</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Type</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Type of DNS entry<br>
<strong>A</strong> =  Assigns an IPv4 address<br>
<strong>CNAME</strong> = Assigns a different host</p></td>
