<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">The target of the entry.<br>
IP address = The IP address of the plentymarkets system.<br>
CNAME = The address of the AWS load balancer endpoint that provides elastic load balancing, i.e. autoscaling.</p></td>
